{"tid":1269004,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人由6月12號之後就一直唔開心，直到最近開始有抑鬱症病狀","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T16:35:58.000Z","uid":56984,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"0e307f1a55c35b5fbe733063a81f1f523bfe03cd","tid":1269004,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"唉，睇嚟我中咗招"},{"pid":"d5a2e496900fb510148ddea2db3d4ce608308051","tid":1269004,"uid":56984,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:23:26.000Z","msg":"1. 情緒方面<br />\n<br />\n情緒低落<br />\n<br />\n對事物或以往嗜好失去興趣<br />\n<br />\n悲觀<br />\n<br />\n感到無助和絕望<br />\n<br />\n緊張、暴躁、焦慮<br />\n<br />\n2. 身體方面<br />\n<br />\n容易疲倦<br />\n<br />\n食慾不振或飲食過量<br />\n<br />\n體重下降或增加<br />\n<br />\n睡眠困擾<br />\n<br />\n性慾減低<br />\n<br />\n多種原因不明的身體不適，如頭痛、腸胃不適、慢性疼痛<br />\n<br />\n3. 思想方面<br />\n<br />\n記憶力退減<br />\n<br />\n難以集中精神<br />\n<br />\n思考困難<br />\n<br />\n缺乏自信<br />\n<br />\n難作決定<br />\n<br />\n過分自責、自疚<br />\n<br />\n有自殺傾向<br />\n<br />\n4. 行為方面<br />\n<br />\n孤僻、不願參與活動<br />\n<br />\n反應變得緩慢<br />\n<br />\n無心打扮<br />\n<br />\n缺乏活力、無法享受人生"},{"pid":"5b175a7a9d007c4dc6e2bd305a0c0cad89ebda98","tid":1269004,"uid":136115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:25:26.000Z","msg":"同路人，有咩就講出嚟"},{"pid":"3b00d6947b45a1f59c1df9b6206f54d9bbc43a02","tid":1269004,"uid":184379,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0e307f1a55c35b5fbe733063a81f1f523bfe03cd","tid":1269004,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"唉，睇嚟我中咗招"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:29:12.000Z","msg":"玩少d電話<br />\n出去行下啦"},{"pid":"8dba2d675c2701993c44f56ab9fcc68ebb4f6ee9","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:46:46.000Z","msg":"我覺得好辛苦，依家坐喺地鐵站到，介唔介意傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bdd9e25f63ff765b8c57eb8caf2978e83ca230e","tid":1269004,"uid":199911,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:50:24.000Z","msg":"有情緒有壓力係正常 記得要揾方法宣洩 唔好一個人收收埋埋"},{"pid":"baaa07907dbaeab247ae90ba17a6087c28e8338b","tid":1269004,"uid":170244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:51:18.000Z","msg":"搵社工/心理學家/精神科,唔好拖<br />\n但要記住you are not alone"},{"pid":"84497f1daff0459a5dfc1b5a16bc97140d2e30ea","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:55:09.000Z","msg":"我想講我本黎聽朝去，但晏晝睇到又有人跳樓，同埋廢佬暴行，所以打算今晚放工就去，老母就想我返屋企，朝早先去。因為咁同老竇老母噪，老竇叫我唔洗返屋企，依家戇鳩鳩坐咗喺地鐵站，好無助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2536ec6fc2bdf21a940dac1ad2d09670b2b0c78","tid":1269004,"uid":68217,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:58:13.000Z","msg":"認真巴打真係要先停止幾日接觸相關資訊...唔好上連登/fb/tg<br />\n再咁落去真係唔會係好事"},{"pid":"ff26689f9f125a4bfb138026e6de0d119330fccd","tid":1269004,"uid":250979,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:59:20.000Z","msg":"真係有。。。。"},{"pid":"dbf009119d0ccee969dfb52d9741599f88985848","tid":1269004,"uid":127451,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:00:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8daaa3d8ab15e4ea5fa157eae5e0c32ef70d0f82","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:01:20.000Z","msg":"咁我依家仲去唔去，出面啲po話29號晩出先救到"},{"pid":"67718614f8ac37ef826585896f3cfc2187f6ff16","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:02:41.000Z","msg":"好想幫手，但家庭壓力真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0869a0828c9fd02f4b098337dda1deeae9815e56","tid":1269004,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:03:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b65e7803c938de446db09be689c8b455d1972d8","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住，我今晚真係好需要大家嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15e1a9949cbb893714aee4a91a77a85bae742b13","tid":1269004,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b65e7803c938de446db09be689c8b455d1972d8","tid":1269004,"uid":55628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T13:08:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對唔住，我今晚真係好需要大家嘅建議<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T18:20:30.000Z","msg":"一齊傾下，救得一個得一個"},{"pid":"4afce96599303059858d0d6fc8a0723e9baff7f4","tid":1269004,"uid":122513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e307f1a55c35b5fbe733063a81f1f523bfe03cd","tid":1269004,"uid":56984,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:22:21.000Z","msg":"唉，睇嚟我中咗招"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T09:41:24.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，<a href=\"http://到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%88%B0%E6%88%91%E5%80%91%E7%9A%84%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99www.help4suicide.com.hk&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXHWT%2F8u5gjw5w0zJU6lVJ48%3D&h=f33d6b88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"a9e786bacfea2c8b28b5906d92a1b0804ac621cd","tid":1269004,"uid":274837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T16:35:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}